{"title":"MySQL基础","uid":"4a207b7e885fdbcca8129599135e5f2e","slug":"MySQL基础","date":"2025-08-14T10:47:38.000Z","updated":"2025-08-14T12:42:18.818Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/MySQL基础.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h1 id=\"MySQL数据库\"><a href=\"#MySQL数据库\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"MySQL数据库\"></a>MySQL数据库</h1><h2 id=\"一、MySQL-是什么？\"><a href=\"#一、MySQL-是什么？\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"一、MySQL 是什么？\"></a>一、MySQL 是什么？</h2><p>MySQL 是一个<strong>开源关系型数据库管理系统</strong>(RDBMS)，由瑞典 MySQL AB 公司开发，现属于 Oracle 旗下产品。它使用结构化查询语言(SQL)进行数据库管理，具有以下核心特性：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>📌 <strong>开源免费</strong>：遵循 GPL 许可</li>\n<li>🚀 <strong>高性能</strong>：支持高并发、快速读写</li>\n<li>🛡️ <strong>可靠性强</strong>：具备事务处理和数据恢复能力</li>\n<li>🌐 <strong>跨平台</strong>：支持 Windows、Linux、macOS 等操作系统</li>\n<li>🔧 <strong>可扩展</strong>：支持多种存储引擎和插件</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"二、核心概念\"><a href=\"#二、核心概念\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"二、核心概念\"></a>二、核心概念</h2><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>概念</th>\n<th>描述</th>\n<th>示例</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>数据库(Database)</strong></td>\n<td>数据存储容器</td>\n<td><code>school_db</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>表(Table)</strong></td>\n<td>结构化数据集合</td>\n<td><code>students</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>列(Column)</strong></td>\n<td>表的字段（数据属性）</td>\n<td><code>name</code>, <code>age</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>行(Row)</strong></td>\n<td>表的数据记录</td>\n<td>一个学生的完整信息</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>主键(PK)</strong></td>\n<td>唯一标识记录的字段</td>\n<td><code>student_id</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>外键(FK)</strong></td>\n<td>关联其他表的关系字段</td>\n<td><code>course_id</code></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h2 id=\"三、SQL-语言基础\"><a href=\"#三、SQL-语言基础\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"三、SQL 语言基础\"></a>三、SQL 语言基础</h2><h3 id=\"1-数据库操作\"><a href=\"#1-数据库操作\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. 数据库操作\"></a>1. 数据库操作</h3><figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">-- 创建数据库</span><br><span class=\"line\">create database school_db;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">-- 使用数据库</span><br><span class=\"line\">use school_db;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">-- 删除数据库</span><br><span class=\"line\">drop database school_db;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">-- 查看有哪些数据库</span><br><span class=\"line\">show databases;  </span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"2-表操作\"><a href=\"#2-表操作\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. 表操作\"></a>2. 表操作</h3><figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">-- 查看当前数据库中有哪些表</span><br><span class=\"line\">show tables; </span><br><span class=\"line\">-- 创建学生表,建立一个名为userlist表格 字段 id 整型  name 字符型 电话 整型  主键值是学号</span><br><span class=\"line\">create table test.userlist (id int,name char(15),tel int,primary key(id));</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">-- 查看表结构</span><br><span class=\"line\">desc students;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"3-数据操作（CRUD）\"><a href=\"#3-数据操作（CRUD）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3. 数据操作（CRUD）\"></a>3. 数据操作（CRUD）</h3><figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">-- 插入数据</span><br><span class=\"line\">insert into test.userlist (id,name,tel) value (1,&#x27;aaa&#x27;,12345678910);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">-- 查询数据</span><br><span class=\"line\">-- 只看 3个字段 而且其中 user字段值为root的内容</span><br><span class=\"line\">select host,user,password from mysql.user where user=&#x27;root&#x27;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">-- 排序查看</span><br><span class=\"line\">select host,user,password from user order by 1;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">-- 更新数据</span><br><span class=\"line\">update test.userlist set tel=&#x27;12341234567&#x27;,sex=&#x27;boy&#x27; where id=1;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">-- 修改数据</span><br><span class=\"line\">-- 在姓名和电话之间加入了性别字段</span><br><span class=\"line\">alter table test.userlist add sex char(10) after name;</span><br><span class=\"line\">-- 修改表结构</span><br><span class=\"line\">alter table test.userlist modify tel char(15);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">-- 删除数据</span><br><span class=\"line\">delete from test.userlist where id=1;</span><br><span class=\"line\">-- 删除表</span><br><span class=\"line\">drop table  test.userlist  </span><br><span class=\"line\">-- 删除数据库</span><br><span class=\"line\">drop database test </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"4-INFORMATION-SCHEMA数据库\"><a href=\"#4-INFORMATION-SCHEMA数据库\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4.INFORMATION_SCHEMA数据库\"></a>4.INFORMATION_SCHEMA数据库</h3><p>INFORMATION_SCHEMA 是 MySQL 中的<strong>元数据库</strong>，它提供了访问数据库元数据的标准化方式。这个特殊的数据库存储了关于 MySQL 服务器维护的所有其他数据库（包括系统数据库）的信息。</p>\n<h4 id=\"核心作用\"><a href=\"#核心作用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"核心作用\"></a>核心作用</h4><ol>\n<li><strong>数据库结构查询</strong>：获取数据库、表、列信息</li>\n<li><strong>权限管理</strong>：查看用户和权限信息</li>\n<li><strong>系统状态监控</strong>：了解服务器运行状态</li>\n<li><strong>约束信息</strong>：获取主键、外键等约束信息</li>\n<li><strong>对象管理</strong>：查看存储过程、函数等</li>\n</ol>\n<h4 id=\"主要组成部分\"><a href=\"#主要组成部分\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"主要组成部分\"></a>主要组成部分</h4><p>以下是 INFORMATION_SCHEMA 中的关键表及其功能：</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>表名</th>\n<th>描述</th>\n<th>常用列</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>SCHEMATA</strong></td>\n<td>所有数据库信息</td>\n<td><code>SCHEMA_NAME</code>, <code>DEFAULT_CHARACTER_SET_NAME</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>TABLES</strong></td>\n<td>所有表信息</td>\n<td><code>TABLE_SCHEMA</code>, <code>TABLE_NAME</code>, <code>ENGINE</code>, <code>TABLE_ROWS</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>COLUMNS</strong></td>\n<td>所有列信息</td>\n<td><code>TABLE_SCHEMA</code>, <code>TABLE_NAME</code>, <code>COLUMN_NAME</code>, <code>DATA_TYPE</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>STATISTICS</strong></td>\n<td>表索引信息</td>\n<td><code>INDEX_NAME</code>, <code>COLUMN_NAME</code>, <code>SEQ_IN_INDEX</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>USER_PRIVILEGES</strong></td>\n<td>用户权限</td>\n<td><code>GRANTEE</code>, <code>PRIVILEGE_TYPE</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>ROUTINES</strong></td>\n<td>存储过程&#x2F;函数</td>\n<td><code>ROUTINE_NAME</code>, <code>ROUTINE_TYPE</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>VIEWS</strong></td>\n<td>视图信息</td>\n<td><code>TABLE_NAME</code>, <code>VIEW_DEFINITION</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>REFERENTIAL_CONSTRAINTS</strong></td>\n<td>外键约束</td>\n<td><code>CONSTRAINT_NAME</code>, <code>UNIQUE_CONSTRAINT_NAME</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>KEY_COLUMN_USAGE</strong></td>\n<td>键约束</td>\n<td><code>CONSTRAINT_NAME</code>, <code>COLUMN_NAME</code>, <code>REFERENCED_TABLE_NAME</code></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h4 id=\"实用查询示例\"><a href=\"#实用查询示例\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实用查询示例\"></a>实用查询示例</h4><h5 id=\"（1）获取所有数据库\"><a href=\"#（1）获取所有数据库\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"（1）获取所有数据库\"></a>（1）获取所有数据库</h5><figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">SELECT SCHEMA_NAME AS &quot;数据库名称&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">FROM INFORMATION_SCHEMA.SCHEMATA;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h5 id=\"（2）查看特定表的结构\"><a href=\"#（2）查看特定表的结构\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"（2）查看特定表的结构\"></a>（2）查看特定表的结构</h5><figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">SELECT </span><br><span class=\"line\">    COLUMN_NAME AS &quot;列名&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    DATA_TYPE AS &quot;数据类型&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    CHARACTER_MAXIMUM_LENGTH AS &quot;最大长度&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    IS_NULLABLE AS &quot;可为空&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">FROM INFORMATION_SCHEMA.COLUMNS</span><br><span class=\"line\">WHERE TABLE_SCHEMA = &#x27;your_database&#x27;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  AND TABLE_NAME = &#x27;your_table&#x27;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h5 id=\"（3）检查表的存储引擎\"><a href=\"#（3）检查表的存储引擎\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"（3）检查表的存储引擎\"></a>（3）检查表的存储引擎</h5><figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">SELECT </span><br><span class=\"line\">    TABLE_NAME AS &quot;表名&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    ENGINE AS &quot;存储引擎&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    TABLE_ROWS AS &quot;行数&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    DATA_LENGTH AS &quot;数据大小(字节)&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">FROM INFORMATION_SCHEMA.TABLES</span><br><span class=\"line\">WHERE TABLE_SCHEMA = &#x27;your_database&#x27;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h5 id=\"（4）查找表的外键约束\"><a href=\"#（4）查找表的外键约束\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"（4）查找表的外键约束\"></a>（4）查找表的外键约束</h5><figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">SELECT </span><br><span class=\"line\">    TABLE_NAME AS &quot;表名&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    COLUMN_NAME AS &quot;外键列&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    REFERENCED_TABLE_NAME AS &quot;引用表&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    REFERENCED_COLUMN_NAME AS &quot;引用列&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">FROM INFORMATION_SCHEMA.KEY_COLUMN_USAGE</span><br><span class=\"line\">WHERE TABLE_SCHEMA = &#x27;your_database&#x27;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  AND REFERENCED_TABLE_NAME IS NOT NULL;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h5 id=\"（5）获取用户权限\"><a href=\"#（5）获取用户权限\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"（5）获取用户权限\"></a>（5）获取用户权限</h5><figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">SELECT </span><br><span class=\"line\">    GRANTEE AS &quot;用户&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    PRIVILEGE_TYPE AS &quot;权限&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    IS_GRANTABLE AS &quot;可授予&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">FROM INFORMATION_SCHEMA.USER_PRIVILEGES</span><br><span class=\"line\">WHERE GRANTEE LIKE &quot;&#x27;your_user&#x27;@&#x27;%&#x27;&quot;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h5 id=\"（6）查看存储过程和函数\"><a href=\"#（6）查看存储过程和函数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"（6）查看存储过程和函数\"></a>（6）查看存储过程和函数</h5><figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">SELECT </span><br><span class=\"line\">    ROUTINE_NAME AS &quot;名称&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    ROUTINE_TYPE AS &quot;类型&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    ROUTINE_DEFINITION AS &quot;定义&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">FROM INFORMATION_SCHEMA.ROUTINES</span><br><span class=\"line\">WHERE ROUTINE_SCHEMA = &#x27;your_database&#x27;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"INFORMATION-SCHEMA-vs-SHOW-COMMANDS\"><a href=\"#INFORMATION-SCHEMA-vs-SHOW-COMMANDS\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"INFORMATION_SCHEMA vs SHOW COMMANDS\"></a>INFORMATION_SCHEMA vs SHOW COMMANDS</h4><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>特性</th>\n<th>INFORMATION_SCHEMA</th>\n<th>SHOW 命令</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>标准化</td>\n<td>SQL标准的一部分</td>\n<td>MySQL特有</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>灵活性</td>\n<td>可使用SQL查询</td>\n<td>固定格式</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>过滤能力</td>\n<td>WHERE条件过滤</td>\n<td>LIKE模式匹配</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>排序能力</td>\n<td>ORDER BY排序</td>\n<td>有限排序</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>应用开发</td>\n<td>更适合程序访问</td>\n<td>适合交互式使用</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<p>示例对比：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">-- SHOW命令</span><br><span class=\"line\">SHOW TABLES FROM your_database LIKE &#x27;user%&#x27;;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">-- INFORMATION_SCHEMA等效</span><br><span class=\"line\">SELECT TABLE_NAME </span><br><span class=\"line\">FROM INFORMATION_SCHEMA.TABLES </span><br><span class=\"line\">WHERE TABLE_SCHEMA = &#x27;your_database&#x27;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  AND TABLE_NAME LIKE &#x27;user%&#x27;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"重要注意事项\"><a href=\"#重要注意事项\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"重要注意事项\"></a>重要注意事项</h4><ol>\n<li><strong>只读特性</strong>：INFORMATION_SCHEMA表是虚拟表，不能修改</li>\n<li><strong>权限要求</strong>：需要SELECT权限访问</li>\n<li><strong>性能影响</strong>：某些查询可能影响性能（如查询TABLE_ROWS）</li>\n<li><strong>实时性</strong>：元数据更新不是实时的（需要ANALYZE TABLE更新统计信息）</li>\n<li><strong>版本差异</strong>：不同MySQL版本表结构有微小差异</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"四、常用数据类型\"><a href=\"#四、常用数据类型\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"四、常用数据类型\"></a>四、常用数据类型</h2><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>类型</th>\n<th>说明</th>\n<th>示例</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>INT</strong></td>\n<td>整数类型</td>\n<td><code>age INT</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>VARCHAR</strong></td>\n<td>可变长度字符串</td>\n<td><code>name VARCHAR(50)</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>DATE</strong></td>\n<td>日期（YYYY-MM-DD）</td>\n<td><code>birthdate DATE</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>DATETIME</strong></td>\n<td>日期时间</td>\n<td><code>register_time DATETIME</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>DECIMAL</strong></td>\n<td>精确小数</td>\n<td><code>score DECIMAL(5,2)</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>ENUM</strong></td>\n<td>枚举值</td>\n<td><code>gender ENUM(&#39;M&#39;,&#39;F&#39;)</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>TEXT</strong></td>\n<td>长文本数据</td>\n<td><code>description TEXT</code></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h2 id=\"五、约束与索引\"><a href=\"#五、约束与索引\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"五、约束与索引\"></a>五、约束与索引</h2><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>约束类型</th>\n<th>说明</th>\n<th>示例</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>PRIMARY KEY</strong></td>\n<td>唯一标识记录</td>\n<td><code>id INT PRIMARY KEY</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>FOREIGN KEY</strong></td>\n<td>关联其他表</td>\n<td><code>FOREIGN KEY (dept_id) REFERENCES departments(id)</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>UNIQUE</strong></td>\n<td>确保字段值唯一</td>\n<td><code>email VARCHAR(100) UNIQUE</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>NOT NULL</strong></td>\n<td>禁止空值</td>\n<td><code>name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>AUTO_INCREMENT</strong></td>\n<td>自增数值（整数主键）</td>\n<td><code>id INT AUTO_INCREMENT</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>INDEX</strong></td>\n<td>加速查询</td>\n<td><code>INDEX idx_name (name)</code></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h2 id=\"六、核心函数\"><a href=\"#六、核心函数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"六、核心函数\"></a>六、核心函数</h2><h3 id=\"1-聚合函数\"><a href=\"#1-聚合函数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. 聚合函数\"></a>1. 聚合函数</h3><figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">SELECT </span><br><span class=\"line\">    COUNT(*) AS total_students,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    AVG(score) AS avg_score,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    MAX(score) AS max_score,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    SUM(score) AS total_scores</span><br><span class=\"line\">FROM exam_results;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"2-字符串函数\"><a href=\"#2-字符串函数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. 字符串函数\"></a>2. 字符串函数</h3><figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">SELECT </span><br><span class=\"line\">    UPPER(name) AS upper_name,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    CONCAT(name, &#x27;(&#x27;, age, &#x27;)&#x27;) AS info,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    LENGTH(address) AS addr_length</span><br><span class=\"line\">FROM students;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"3-日期函数\"><a href=\"#3-日期函数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3. 日期函数\"></a>3. 日期函数</h3><figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">SELECT </span><br><span class=\"line\">    name,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    DATEDIFF(CURDATE(), birthdate)/365 AS age_years,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    DATE_FORMAT(birthdate, &#x27;%Y年%m月%d日&#x27;) AS birth_cn</span><br><span class=\"line\">FROM students;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"七、关系与连接\"><a href=\"#七、关系与连接\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"七、关系与连接\"></a>七、关系与连接</h2><figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">-- 创建关联表</span><br><span class=\"line\">CREATE TABLE courses (</span><br><span class=\"line\">    id INT PRIMARY KEY,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    name VARCHAR(50)</span><br><span class=\"line\">);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">CREATE TABLE enrollments (</span><br><span class=\"line\">    student_id INT,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    course_id INT,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    FOREIGN KEY (student_id) REFERENCES students(id),</span><br><span class=\"line\">    FOREIGN KEY (course_id) REFERENCES courses(id)</span><br><span class=\"line\">);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">-- 多表连接查询</span><br><span class=\"line\">SELECT </span><br><span class=\"line\">    s.name AS student_name,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    c.name AS course_name</span><br><span class=\"line\">FROM students s</span><br><span class=\"line\">JOIN enrollments e ON s.id = e.student_id</span><br><span class=\"line\">JOIN courses c ON e.course_id = c.id;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"八、存储引擎对比\"><a href=\"#八、存储引擎对比\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"八、存储引擎对比\"></a>八、存储引擎对比</h2><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>引擎</th>\n<th>事务支持</th>\n<th>锁机制</th>\n<th>外键支持</th>\n<th>应用场景</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>InnoDB</strong></td>\n<td>✅</td>\n<td>行级锁</td>\n<td>✅</td>\n<td>主要生产环境</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>MyISAM</strong></td>\n<td>❌</td>\n<td>表级锁</td>\n<td>❌</td>\n<td>只读&#x2F;低并发</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Memory</strong></td>\n<td>❌</td>\n<td>表级锁</td>\n<td>❌</td>\n<td>临时表&#x2F;缓存数据</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h2 id=\"九、实用工具\"><a href=\"#九、实用工具\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"九、实用工具\"></a>九、实用工具</h2><ol>\n<li><p><strong>mysql 命令行客户端</strong>：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mysql -uroot -ppassword</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>MySQL Workbench</strong>：官方图形化管理工具</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>phpMyAdmin</strong>：Web 版数据库管理工具</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>MySQL Shell</strong>：高级命令行工具（支持 JavaScript、Python）</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"十、学习路径建议\"><a href=\"#十、学习路径建议\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"十、学习路径建议\"></a>十、学习路径建议</h2><ol>\n<li>基础阶段：<ul>\n<li>数据库&#x2F;表操作</li>\n<li>基本 CRUD 语句</li>\n<li>数据类型和约束</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>中级阶段：<ul>\n<li>多表连接查询</li>\n<li>聚合函数与分组</li>\n<li>视图与存储过程</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>高级阶段：<ul>\n<li>索引优化</li>\n<li>事务与锁机制</li>\n<li>备份恢复策略</li>\n<li>主从复制</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n","text":"MySQL数据库一、MySQL 是什么？MySQL 是一个开源关系型数据库管理系统(RDBMS)，由瑞典 MySQL AB 公司开发，现属于 Oracle 旗下...","permalink":"/post/MySQL基础","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"6k","symbolsTime":"5 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"MySQL数据库","slug":"MySQL数据库","count":1,"path":"api/tags/MySQL数据库.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#MySQL%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93\"><span class=\"toc-text\">MySQL数据库</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%80%E3%80%81MySQL-%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%EF%BC%9F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">一、MySQL 是什么？</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BA%8C%E3%80%81%E6%A0%B8%E5%B